modName: Original Serana and Valerica - For Botox users
summary:
If you have a BOTOX mod and want to keep Serana and Valerica Vanilla... This mod is for you
No esp, only loose files
descriptionHtml:
If you have a BOTOX mod - [url=http://https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89635]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89635[/url]
and want to keep Serana and Valerica Vanilla... This mod is for you

Everybody have different tastes and personally I like Vanilla Serana and Valerica because with my texture set they look just better :) For me Vanilla appearance of some NPCs have unique character...



Maybe I did in future some more NPC's which look better in Vanilla style
Just post NPC name you wanna keep VANILLA [ via thispage or something [url=http://elderscrolls.wikia.com/wiki/Skyrim]http://elderscrolls.wikia.com/wiki/Skyrim[/url]] and maybe I did a mod with this NPC to restore original appearance :)
author: Tujestem
